title: Draft Prospects with the Highest Ceiling & Chasing the Chiefs in the AFC West
itunes:title: Draft Prospects with the Highest Ceiling & Chasing the Chiefs in the AFC West
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys discuss the draft prospects with the highest ceiling by position (2:32). Then, the duo look at the potential run on wide receivers from picks 11 to 21 in the draft (20:30). Next, the pair talk about the difficulties of evaluating prospects who don't play in the best circumstances (25:30). To wrap up the show, the guys explain the challenges teams face in the AFC West while trying to catch up to the Chiefs (30:13).
